<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-01-0680 </DOCNO><TEXT>This guide gives an understanding of the OSHA Hazard Communication Standardwhich regulates hazardous materials in the workplace. Contents include:how to identify hazards in the workplace; characterization of hazards;label design and content; written hazard communication program; employeetraining; legal responsibilities including penalties and consequences;and a MSDS form.</TEXT></DOC>